    <summary type="html">&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;When I started playing D&amp;amp;D back in my mid teens and the early 1980s I
did not particularly like the artwork of Erol Otus.  I think at the
time I preferred more realistic artwork.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When I got back into playing D&amp;amp;D regularly with 3.5E, I also started
looking back at the older versions of D&amp;amp;D, and found that I now really
liked Erol Otus's artwork.  I think it is the fever dream aspect of it
that I like.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So, my enjoyment of Otus's work has nothing to do with nostalgia.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</summary>
